Jarvis/
│
├── Speech I/O
│   ├── listen()          → Microphone speech → text
│   └── speak()           → text → Edge Neural TTS
│
├── Command Router
│   └── execute()         → Matches command to actions
│
├── System Control
│   ├── volume, brightness, wifi, bluetooth
│   ├── lock, shutdown, restart
│   └── window management
│
├── File Manager
│   └── create/delete/move/copy/rename/search
│
├── Utilities
│   └── screenshot, clipboard, typing, keypress
│
├── AI Model Handler
│   └── ask_ai() → communicates with local mistral model
│
├── GUI (PyQt5)
│   └── JarvisGUI class
│
└── Main Loop
    └── start_jarvis()  → Wake-word detection (“Jarvis”)
